  "prompt": "Why did Akshay Kumar take up Canadian citizenship?",
  "response": "Akshay Kumar, the popular Bollywood actor, took up Canadian citizenship in 2011. He has explained his decision by saying that he wanted to ensure a better future for his child. Kumar has also mentioned that the Canadian citizenship process was relatively straightforward, and he appreciated the lifestyle and opportunities in Canada. Despite his Canadian citizenship, he has continued to work in the Indian film industry and maintains a strong connection to India. His choice has sometimes been a topic of discussion, especially regarding patriotism, but he has stated that his commitment to his work in Indian cinema remains unchanged.",
